IMMEDIATELY INVOKED FUNCTIONS EXPRESSIONS (IIFE)S

function greet(name) {
    console.log("Hello " + name);
}

greet();


USING A FUNCTION EXPRESSION
var greetFunction = function(name) {
    console.log("Hello" + name);
};
greetFunction("John");

USING AN IMMEDIATELY INVOKED FUNCTION EXPRESSION (IIFE)
var greetFunction = function(name) {
    return "Hello" + name;
}("John");


TO INVOKE A FUNCTION STATEMENT WITHOUT A VARIABLE
(function(name) {
  return "Hello " + name;
}("Yes"));
